{"statement":{"language":"es","images":[],"sources":[],"markdown":"# Descripci\u00f3n\n\nDados dos enteros $m$ y $n$, escribe un programa que construya una matriz con $m$ renglones y $n$ columnas cuyas entradas sean los n\u00fameros $1, 2, \\ldots, mn$ acomodados en diagonal, comenzando con el $1$ en la entrada que est\u00e1 en la esquina superior izquierda, siguiendo con el $2$ a la derecha del $1$ y el $3$ abajo del $1$, y as\u00ed sucesivamente.\n\n# Entrada\n\nDos n\u00fameros enteros $2 \\leq m, n \\leq 100$, separados por un espacio.\n\n# Salida\n\nLa matriz requerida (ver el ejemplo de salida para el formato).\n\n# Ejemplo\n\n||input\n3 5\n||output\n1  2  4  7 10\n3  5  8 11 13\n6  9 12 14 15\n||end\n"},"settings":{"cases":{"statement_001":{"in":"3 5","out":"1  2  4  7 10\n3  5  8 11 13\n6  9 12 14 15","weight":1}},"limits":{"ExtraWallTime":"0s","MemoryLimit":33554432,"OutputLimit":32768,"OverallWallTimeLimit":"1m0s","TimeLimit":"1s"},"validator":{"name":"token-caseless"}},"problem_id":1030,"title":"Matriz con entradas en diagonal","alias":"med","input_limit":10240,"visits":41,"submissions":739,"accepted":142,"difficulty":1.112331491551373,"creation_date":1396624702,"source":"UAM Azcapotzalco 2005","order":"normal","visibility":2,"email_clarifications":false,"allow_user_add_tags":true,"show_diff":"none","quality_seal":true,"version":"6e3fdaa57c33df7a33dfb94c22a4345bd2ff3af0","commit":"65e01a1c0e1905d806fe2bf1377bcd0b6185fba7","nominationStatus":{"alreadyReviewed":false,"dismissed":false,"dismissedBeforeAc":false,"nominated":false,"nominatedBeforeAc":false,"language":"","canNominateProblem":false,"solved":false,"tried":false},"problemsetter":{"username":"rcc","classname":"user-rank-international-master","name":"rcc","creation_date":1396624702},"languages":["c11-gcc","c11-clang","cpp11-gcc","cpp11-clang","cpp17-gcc","cpp17-clang","java","py2","py3","rb","cs","pas","hs","lua"],"accepts_submissions":true,"karel_problem":false,"limits":{"input_limit":"10 KiB","mem